data.description: This well-maintained home offers a spacious interior, perfect for accommodating your family's needs. With a thoughtful layout, the property boasts a comfortable living space and four generously sized bedrooms.  While the home is in good condition, there's potential for you to add your personal touch and increase its value with a bit of elbow grease. Bring your creativity and envision the possibilities to make this space truly your own.  The property's location provides easy access to local amenities, schools, and parks, making it an ideal choice for families. Take advantage of this opportunity to invest in a home with great bones and customize it to suit your unique style.
